{"type":"message","id":"3bf942b8","parentId":"7bd0160f","timestamp":"2026-04-10T09:58:41.103Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"When you give me a task, I start by reading these files in my workspace:\n\n1. **SOUL.md** - Defines who I am and my tone.\n2. **USER.md** - Details about you, so I can help you better.\n3. **TOOLS.md** - Lists tools and skills available for the task.\n4. **skill-specific files**, as needed for the task (e.g., email sending rules).\n5. **HEARTBEAT.md** - For periodic task handling.\n6. **MEMORY.md** or relevant daily memory files - For continuity with past sessions.\n\nThis ensures I approach each request with full context. What’s your next command?"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"github-copilot","model":"gpt-4o","usage":{"input":17801,"output":139,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":17940,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775815116888,"responseId":"chatcmpl-DT2vHdcDYZBokCfOQqqF5iIyVl318"}}
